text: Goodou gu hagabagi gi daha digau hai mee dabu a Dimaadua, ala go nia hagadili o Aaron, gei goodou gu hagabagi digau Levi. I nadau lohongo, goodou guu bida dongo godou gau hai mee dabu gadoo be di hai o nnenua llauehe ala i golo. Di ingoo hua tangada dela ma ga gaamai dana kau daane be nia siibi e hidu e mee hua di hagadabu e mogobuna di hai tangada hai mee dabu o nia god ala e hagaingoo go goodou bolo godou god.
